#: ../nitropc/index.rst:28
msgid ""
"Connect the USB drive to a black USB 2.0 socket (blue USB 3.0 don't "
"work!), start the PC and keep pressing DEL until you see the firmware "
"menu. Choose Boot Menu and select your USB drive."
